#29001
#rAkuma#n's Office in the #PBouncing Bosom Tavern#n~
This small office is a barren place.  In the middle of the room is a small desk,
with a very comfortable looking chair behind it.  On top of this desk is almost
nothing, just a small name plate that reads "Akuma, Head CEO".  On the walls are
two framed documents.  One seems to be a deed to the Bouncing Bosoms Tavern.
The other is an archaic document which reads "Akuma, on this blessed day, has
led the mighty elven forces of Aramul toward victory against the evil human
empire of 'SennaNight'.  All hail Lord Akuma, reclaimer of 859 gold pieces."
All in all, this is a rather strange room.  Also you notice a recent addition to
the room.  Behind the desk, in one corner of the room is a large bed.  The soft,
silk sheets are rumpled, the bed unmade, and the light around the bed is
slightly dimmer then the ever-present light of the rest of the room.  Barely
visible through the darkness surrounding the bed, there seems to be a word
engraved into the footboard...
~
