#29006
Dude's Bassoon Studio~
This room is a scene of complete disorganization. The floor has been 
nearly covered with cane shavings. Pieces of music lie scattered all 
around the room from the wiesenborn etude book, to the Mozart 
bassoon concerto and the stadio excerpt book. A large table holds an 
odd variety of tools. Some of the tools are fairly common, knives, 
pliers, files, but some of the others can only be described as, 
strange. A large book entitled "Treatise on the Battle Versus Pure 
Evil" lies on the desk. A bassoon lies set up on a stand in one of 
the corners of the room.
~
